FROM golang:1.17.5-bullseye

ARG TAG

ENV GOPATH /go

COPY . ${GOPATH}/src/github.com/mosuka/phalanx

RUN apt-get update \
    && apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y \
       build-essential \
    && apt-get clean \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN cd ${GOPATH}/src/github.com/mosuka/phalanx \
    && make TAG=${TAG} build


FROM debian:bullseye-slim
